=======================
{ fourtyeight.library }
=======================

a store for all the posts that users make. each document
contains everything we need to display, the user, timestamp
post details and comments. 

### schema 
  
  Document = {
    last_updated: 347324566 
    post: Post, 
    comments: [Post]
  }

  Post = {
    owner: 1, 
    image: "http://url.to.image/",
    text: "a string with about a len ~= 2000"
  }
